FT  26 NOV 94 / Weekend Money (Financial Planning): A reader writes
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
While on holiday in France in the summer at EuroDisney, its staff made two
separate errors while processing payments on my Visa card. Both required
credits to be made.
When I got my statement, however, I noticed there was a loading of around 5
per cent on these credits. On querying this, I received a further credit. I
then found that a friend had exactly the same problem on a holiday in the US
 -also involving Disney.
I wonder if other readers have had similar experiences.
AJ Fuller
Heath and Reach
Bedfordshire
