A group of creditors led by New York investment bank Goldman Sachs has
proposed a financial restructuring of Cadillac Fairview, the troubled
Canadian property group owning significant downtown office buildings and
shopping centres and assets of about CDollars 4.5bn (USDollars 3.3bn),
